      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">If one of the DC input becomes unavailable in a system with
a 2N configuration, the other dc input will still supply one group
of modules. One group modules is enough to supply the full load. The
group modules can be N, N+1, N+x or N+N.</p>
